Open Standard License — SVARE Reference Implementation

SVARE — Structural Value Resolution Engine (Correctness Without Computation)
Shunyaya Structural Resolution Model

---

Legal Status

This license is a permissive Open Standard license for the SVARE reference implementation.

To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, this license grants rights similar in spirit to permissive open-source licenses, while preserving truthful representation requirements for the SVARE name and reference implementation.

If any provision is found unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.

---

Nature of Release

This is a minimal, self-contained reference implementation.

It is intended to demonstrate a structural value correctness model — not to represent a full arithmetic system, symbolic mathematics engine, or computational framework.

Behavioral guarantees apply only within the scope of the reference model and its defined structural assumptions.

