---

Closing Statement

SVARE explores a simple but fundamental idea:

Value correctness emerges deterministically from structure, without computation, arithmetic execution, or evaluation pipelines.

Computation may reveal value.  
It does not determine it.

It is released to encourage:

• independent validation  
• real-world testing  
• safe experimentation  

SVARE is offered as a minimal reference implementation of that possibility.
